        "header": "2Related Work",
        "images": [
            {
                "img": "https://arxiv.org/html/2510.04290/x2.png",
                "caption": "Figure 3:Overview of the ChronoEdit pipeline.From right to left, the denoising process begins in thetemporal reasoning stage, where the model imagines and denoises a short trajectory of intermediate frames. These intermediate frames act as reasoning tokens, guiding how the edit should unfold in a physically consistent manner. For efficiency, the reasoning tokens are discarded in the subsequentediting frame generation stage, where the target frame is further refined into the final edited image.",
                "position": 200
            }
        ]
